Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.02,0:02:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Countless pirates fight\Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the great treasure left behind\Nby Gold Roger, the Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.79,0:03:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body\Nturned to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.63,0:03:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,also takes to the sea\Nto become the next Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,As Luffy and his friends\Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the World Government is less and less\Nable to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.45,0:03:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What adventure is waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.18,0:03:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.03,0:03:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,After losing his brother Ace during \Nthe Paramount War against the Navy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy was consumed with unbearable sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.54,0:03:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There is, however, an untold \Nstory of the brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...10 years ago in the East \NBlue - Luffy and Ace as boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.05,0:03:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo who became brother to Luffy and Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.45,0:03:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...has been brought home by \Nhis father, a member of the nobility.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:04:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do as you say. I'll \Nlive as you want so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.86,0:04:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...please don't hurt these two!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.57,0:04:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you. They're very important \Nto me, they're my brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.61,0:04:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We all have to keep quiet about the plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What if someone outside the \Ntown finds out about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.35,0:04:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We're special! If you're \Nfrom a noble family...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.09,0:04:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! Ace! Luffy!
