Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I know. What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.55,0:05:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They're setting boxes of oil and explosives all over Gray Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I have to tell them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you! Watch out! You have to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.94,0:05:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,--We got him!\N--Hey, relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Burn down Gray Terminal?! Why are you doing that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool! Don't scream! We can't \Nlet anyone else know about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.43,0:05:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is serious! I gotta tell everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a bad guy just as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to not to scream. \NHey, hold them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.30,0:05:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the mastermind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.01,0:06:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There was oil and explosives in the boxes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that you guys carried yesterday and today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.15,0:06:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's gonna be a massive \Nfire that no one can escape from.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.89,0:06:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,--No...\N--Are you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Even punk kids like you two are freaking out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.09,0:06:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But now you know about the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.80,0:06:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to ask you something before the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.71,0:06:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, you two, do you have a \Ntreasure hidden away somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.45,0:06:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You've given me nothing but \Ntrouble! You're such a bad son!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.19,0:06:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I was right to adopt another \Nchild just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.50,0:06:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Open up, dad! I gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.23,0:07:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There are people that I have \Nto help! Dad! Dad! Open Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.58,0:07:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I...!
