Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:07:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's wrong with Gray Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.03,0:08:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it burning?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the best game I've ever played!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,B-B-Boss! Boss! You gotta see this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.08,0:08:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you screaming about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,--The sky in the north, look!\N--Is it the town?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No, closer than that!\NMust be Gray Terminal! It's on fire!
