Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:26.16,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,What's going on? It's like a wildfire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's never happened before!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous - evacuate Edge Town!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:36.63,Sign,,0,0,260,,{\blur0.3\fad(500,0)\fs77\bord2.3\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(455,500,\1a&H00&)}Edge Town, Great Gate
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.00,0:08:36.63,Sign,,0,0,260,,{\blur0.3\fad(500,0)\fs77\bord0\4a&HFF&}Edge Town, Great Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:36.10,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,All residents must head to Midtown!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the lifesaving and fire \Nextinguishing to us military!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,--We made it to the Great Gate!\N--We're safe now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.51,0:08:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.98,0:08:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We only protect the residents here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,--No way!\N--How can you do this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,--Let us get in!\N--Help us, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,--Everybody, wake up!\N--You gotta run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,--The fire is spreading all around!\N--We can't stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use, give it up! \NYou gotta flee your home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.66,0:09:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! The fire has gotten to the shore already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The entrance to the forest is ablaze, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! Where should we go?! We're stuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn everything, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.74,0:09:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,When we complete this task,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.95,0:09:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,my long-cherished dream will come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't give a damn \Nabout the other people living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But even if this place is so crappy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it's good enough for us to hide in, King.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm aware of that, Bluejam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.93,0:10:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But when this is over, you \Nno longer need to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.20,0:10:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I will make you and your friends \Nnobles by my authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.65,0:10:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The king will give us titles
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.08,0:10:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll live in the High \NTown as privileged nobles!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We better get moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get to the Great Gate! \NThe military is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.27,0:10:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, we left the brats in the hideout...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.97,0:10:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget 'em. They could've joined my crew \Nif they told me where the treasure was.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.28,0:11:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Fools can't live long anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's closed, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't panic. They just don't \Nwant other people to get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.59,0:11:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan is for me to give them a sign, \Nthen they'll open the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.89,0:11:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Bluejam. Open up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.28,0:11:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys, what are \Nyou doing?! Open the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.88,0:11:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan was you let us \Nevacuate from here, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not what we agreed to! You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.36,0:11:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to your promise, King?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that you'd make us nobles...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.70,0:11:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You set us up? King!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.10,0:12:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Bluejam, a pirate in Gray Terminal, started the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought! \NNo one else would do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.85,0:12:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it to try to keep the observers \Nfrom the World Government away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How terrible he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.19,0:12:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot! It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! We didn't wanna be involved in this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.73,0:12:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't get away! I don't wanna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.67,0:12:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave you behind if \Nyou don't stop complaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, it's hot! No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The fire is everywhere outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.25,0:12:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The air is hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.52,0:12:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be alright! I'm here with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.82,0:12:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Call the police! Sabo did it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:13:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.53,0:13:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?! You have to evacuate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.04,0:13:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.61,0:13:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.38,0:13:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.38,0:13:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.02,0:13:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away! Stay away from the lock!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.23,0:13:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.36,0:13:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,--Be a good kid and evacuate!\N--Don't give us any trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.08,0:13:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Ace... Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.94,0:14:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.68,0:14:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The royalty and nobles \Nare... behind the fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.92,0:14:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.03,0:14:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This town smells worse than Gray Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.87,0:14:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It smells like rotten people!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If I stay here... I'll never be free!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:15:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...ashamed of being born a noble!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.85,0:15:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They finally made a kid \Nsay this! Goa Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.73,0:15:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how you feel. I was \Nborn in this country, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still don't have enough \Npower to change the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.20,0:15:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man, you really are \Nlistening to me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and I'll never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.52,0:15:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.51,0:16:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No... No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, there's no chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.13,0:16:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way to put out the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.90,0:16:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta give up the ship! \NWe can't flee to the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.57,0:16:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn the King! How could he do this to us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.37,0:16:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show that bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.94,0:16:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.28,0:16:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so annoying that the sky \Nin the south is bright even in the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We are sorry, your Majesty. \NLet us close the curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, daddy, why are the people in Gray Terminal not humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:17:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do they have to get burned?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,As the phrase goes, "As a \Nman sows, so shall he reap."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They could have avoided their \Nfate just by being born nobles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Born nobles?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.28,0:17:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right! They should have \Nchosen to be born nobles!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They're stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, enough about those people, \Nyou have to study for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You better go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.76,0:17:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.32,0:17:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,--There's no way on this side!\N--We keep losing ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if those old men escaped safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:18:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no time to be concerned \Nabout other people!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! I don't even know where I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said that you could get away, you brats?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Bluejam!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.21,0:18:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you still here \Nafter setting the fire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.31,0:18:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You were supposed to have escaped by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.92,0:18:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We're hopeless, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.46,0:18:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We have an unforeseen dilemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans are strange creatures, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.56,0:18:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When you hit rock bottom, \Nyou can't stop laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They are acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.88,0:18:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:19:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We worked together - we're friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.59,0:19:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to die together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't wanna die with you! \NNot in a million years!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, you haven't told \Nme where you keep your treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll save it for you before the fire \Ngets it. So tell me where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life is in danger and all \Nyou care about is treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.98,0:19:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't care, then tell me where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.09,0:19:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gone mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.52,0:19:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not gonna go \Nget it, it'd be a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.13,0:19:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If nothing is done, it's gonna be \Nreduced to charcoal like my ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.37,0:19:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.17,0:19:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous! That treasure is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace! You and Sabo spent a lot of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.38,0:19:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo would understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.68,0:19:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What matters the most now is your...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What matters the most now is our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.13,0:20:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We keep our treasure from \Nlast 6 years in this tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.21,0:20:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.51,0:20:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright. This is not the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.79,0:20:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?! I told you where it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.49,0:20:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. This is not the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.33,0:20:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means you could be lying. \NYou gotta come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Then it's gonna \Nbe too late to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.74,0:20:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you guys go on your own?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:21:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't wanna mess with me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm determined to make a come back,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.62,0:21:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,even if it means stealing from kids
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.85,0:21:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,so I can take my revenge on nobles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And your brother is one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.06,0:21:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They think they're so special
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and look down on others as if we're trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sabo doesn't think like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.87,0:21:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the same as them, fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.27,0:21:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He was with you both just to feel superior!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.41,0:21:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.84,0:21:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,His parents are loaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't \Nhave to worry about anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just a pastime for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.79,0:21:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He was looking down on you guys
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.86,0:21:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and laughing to himself holding his nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.59,0:21:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop talking bad about Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.23,0:21:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Sabo just wants to be free!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.53,0:21:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.37,0:21:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.61,0:22:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.32,0:22:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch Luffy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.78,0:22:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy! You okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.48,0:22:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.66,0:22:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.46,0:22:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You creepy brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.39,0:23:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you wanna make a fool out of me, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.23,0:23:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you scumbag!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.53,0:23:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.70,0:23:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.64,0:23:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.45,0:23:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace and Luffy are cornered by Bluejam!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.62,0:23:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Trapped among the flames with no escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.36,0:23:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace stands his ground and \Nprepares to fight alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.29,0:23:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, left behind in High Town,
